OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome evening
OL,6,Fsunny spells before cloud increasing
OL,7,Ffrom the north. Band of rain, perhaps
OL,8,Fheavy at times, moving south
OL,9,Fovernight. Becoming breezy at times
OL,10,Fwith very strong winds along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FLargely dry and bright with
OL,13,Fsunny intervals and a few coastal
OL,14,Fshowers. Breezy then easing later,
OL,15,Fthough strong winds near coasts.
OL,16,FClearing skies overnight could see
OL,17,Fsome ground frost patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
