OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBreezy
OL,6,Fand cloudy, with rain Tuesday morning,
OL,7,Ffollowed by showers. Blustery showers,
OL,8,Fwith possible thunder, and sunny
OL,9,Fintervals Wednesday and Thursday. Cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
